n="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin">Current year quarter charges of $35 million ($29 million after tax) were primarily driven by charges related to inventory adjustments and contingent settlements, tax effected using the applicable tax rates. Prior year quarter charges of $54 million pretax ($43 million after tax) were related to restructuring and contingencies, tax effected using the applicable tax rates.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignt" colspan="1" rowspan="1">(c)</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwvertalignt bwpadl0" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin">Current year quarter charges of $55 million was driven by the Company’s share of non-recurring charges related to provisions recorded by Wilmar.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignt" colspan="1" rowspan="1">(d)</td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwvertalignt bwpadl0" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin">Discrete tax adjustment relates to the non-recurring impact of updated tax regulations.</p></td></tr></table><table cellspacing="0" class="bwtablemarginb bwblockalignl bwwidth100"><tr><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="20" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"><b>Return on Invested Capital (ROIC) and Adjusted ROIC</b></p><p class="bwcellpmargin"><b>Non-GAAP financial measures</b></p><p class="bwcellpmargin">(unaudited)</p></td></tr><tr><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="4" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0 bwwidth1" colspan="1" rowspan="1"></td><td class="bwpadl0" colspan="3" rowspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td class="bwvertalignb bwpadl0" colspan="20" rowspan="1"><p class="bwcellpmargin"><b>Adjusted ROIC Earnings (in millions)</b></p></td></tr><tr><td class